Delicious and easy! What could be better? I served a pear trio for Christmas dessert using this sorbet, Pear Spice Cake (without the Pecan Praline Topping) and Pears Poached in Red Wine , Cardamon and Orange-all from Epicurious. It was a hit with everyone, especially my lactose intolerant sister-in-law.

Rating: 3
This turned out really well (and it was the first time I used an ice cream maker as well). I used confectioner's sugar (wasn't sure if that was what was called for, but it worked well) and used about 3/4 of the amount called for. Also, I almost doubled the cardamom (I love cardamom!). This was a very easy and fairly healthy dessert that I highly recommend.

